erties offering accommodation. This aims to enhance tourism infrastructure and provide income opportunities for residents.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/hospitality/delhi-draft-bb-policy-proposes-eight-room-16-bed-limit-cctv-mandatory/131367131?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-99660/131367131.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "hospitality"}]}